transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you for calling Viagra at Score Blue. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Hello, my name is Brett. Can I ask for a refund?

Speaker 1: Okay, sir. Yeah, I can help you with this.

Speaker 2: Can you just provide me with the phone number associated with the account?

Speaker 1: Sure, no problem. My phone number is 765-716-7510.

Speaker 2: Okay, and can you provide me the full name and date of birth, please?

Speaker 1: Yes, my full name is Brett Oller and my date of birth is August 21, 1959.

Speaker 2: So, Brett, your account, it shows here that you called a few weeks ago and you put it on a pause.

Speaker 1: So, it's currently inactive. Can I ask you what has changed?

Speaker 2: If I don't remember, like, I just want to completely cancel it, can you help me?

Speaker 1: I'd like to ask for a refund.

Speaker 2: Well, you called about two weeks ago and there weren't any issues and then you paused your account.

Speaker 1: So, no further charges, right?

Speaker 2: Well, it's paused currently, correct.

Speaker 1: I just want to completely cancel my subscription rather than pause it because I might be able to be charged soon.

Speaker 2: No, you're not set to be charged any time soon.

Speaker 1: Oh, okay. Could you tell me when my service got paused?

Speaker 2: Yeah, currently right now it's paused all the way until August 1.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Hello?

Speaker 1: I see, I see. I don't remember, like, the last bill was on December 15, 1985 for $63.95, right?

Speaker 2: So, that was your last transaction and you called about a month after that to pause it.

Speaker 1: Yeah, actually, can I change? I don't want to pause it.
